cs.MA, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.GT 

Reasoning: 
- cs.MA (Multiagent Systems) is the most likely category as the paper deals with cooperative control of a team of vehicles. 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as the paper discusses the task execution method for each vehicle. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper presents algorithms for task assignment and hierarchical model predictive control. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is relevant as the paper deals with control of a multi-vehicle system. 
- cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory) is less likely but still possible as the paper applies the methods to an adversarial game between two teams of vehicles.
